Command uses
Move into Kafka container
docker exec -it kafka /bin/sh

Go inside kafka installation folder
cd /opt/kafka_2.13-2.8.1/bin

Create Kafka topic
kafka-topics.sh --create --zookeeper zookeeper:2181 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 1 --topic streaming
kafka-topics.sh --create --zookeeper zookeeper:2181 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 1 --topic scored-transactions


Run producer.py to stream

check dtbricks
